gw.api.diff.node

Class RemoveDiffTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.diff.node.AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode
      • gw.api.diff.node.AbstractDiffItemDiffTreeNode
        • gw.api.diff.node.RemoveDiffTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDiffItemTreeNode<AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode>, IDiffTreeNode<AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode>

    public class RemoveDiffTreeNode
extends AbstractDiffItemDiffTreeNode
    A remove row in the difference tree. These rows display the passed description for their Label. They also use the display keys Java.Diff.Existed and Java.Diff.Removed for the Value1 and Value2 columns, respectively.
